e_104hvv1665702546209.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hvv1665702546209.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hvv1665702546209.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hvv1665702546209\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the amount of time an HTTP request can take to complete.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__topic_d133655e1_d133656e1_d133657e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__p_d133658e1_d133659e1_d133660e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UHTTP.SET_TIMEOUT(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Timeout</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__section_brn_pbz_1wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d989846e64\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w115ab1b5b3b3_w116ab1b5b3_w117ab1b5_w118ab1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w115ab1b5b3b3_w116ab1b5b3_w117ab1b5_w118ab1__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w115ab1b5b3b3_w116ab1b5b3_w117ab1b5_w118ab1__entry__2\">Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w115ab1b5b3b3_w116ab1b5b3_w117ab1b5_w118ab1__entry__3\">Direction</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w115ab1b5b3b3_w116ab1b5b3_w117ab1b5_w118ab1__entry__4\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w115ab1b5b3b3_w116ab1b5b3_w117ab1b5_w118ab1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Timeout</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w115ab1b5b3b3_w116ab1b5b3_w117ab1b5_w118ab1__entry__2\">numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w115ab1b5b3b3_w116ab1b5b3_w117ab1b5_w118ab1__entry__3\">IN</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w115ab1b5b3b3_w116ab1b5b3_w117ab1b5_w118ab1__entry__4\">Maximum time allowed for the request in milliseconds.\n                By default it is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code> (no timeout).</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__section_mgv_rbz_1wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d989846e126\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w119ab1b5b5b3_w120ab1b5b5_w121ab1b5_w122ab1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w119ab1b5b5b3_w120ab1b5b5_w121ab1b5_w122ab1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w119ab1b5b5b3_w120ab1b5b5_w121ab1b5_w122ab1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w119ab1b5b5b3_w120ab1b5b5_w121ab1b5_w122ab1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w119ab1b5b5b3_w120ab1b5b5_w121ab1b5_w122ab1__entry__2\">Success</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w119ab1b5b5b3_w120ab1b5b5_w121ab1b5_w122ab1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-12</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w119ab1b5b5b3_w120ab1b5b5_w121ab1b5_w122ab1__entry__2\">Internal error occurred</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w119ab1b5b5b3_w120ab1b5b5_w121ab1b5_w122ab1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-13</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hvv1665702546209__table_w119ab1b5b5b3_w120ab1b5b5_w121ab1b5_w122ab1__entry__2\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Timeout</var> value is not valid</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__section_urs_vbz_1wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d989846e198\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Can be use before the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SEND</span> operation.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hvv1665702546209__section_rrp_xbz_1wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d989846e210\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SET_TIMEOUT</span> operation sets the amount of time a HTTP request can\n        take to complete.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528398\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528398\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "SET_TIMEOUT Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Set the amount of time an HTTP request can take to complete. UHTTP.SET_TIMEOUT( Timeout ) Parameters Parameter Type Direction Description Timeout numeric IN Maximum time allowed for the request in milliseconds. By default it is set to -1 (no timeout). Return Values Table 1. Values returned in $status Value Meaning 0 Success -12 Internal error occurred -13 Timeout value is not valid Use Can be use before the SEND operation. Description The SET_TIMEOUT operation sets the amount of time a HTTP request can take to complete. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}